"-------------------- 自动补全 -----------------------
"使用映射
"inoremap   (   ()<ESC>i
"inoremap   [   []<ESC>i
"inoremap   {   {}<ESC>i
"inoremap   "   ""<ESC>i
"inoremap   '   ''<ESC>i

"设置跳出自动补全的括号
func SkipPair()  
    if getline('.')[col('.') - 1] == ')' || getline('.')[col('.') - 1] == ']' || getline('.')[col('.') - 1] == '"' || getline('.')[col('.') - 1] == "'" || getline('.')[col('.') - 1] == '}'  
        return "\<ESC>la"  
    else  
        return "\t"  
    endif  
endfunc  
" 将tab键绑定为跳出括号  
inoremap <TAB> <c-r>=SkipPair()<CR>


